			<h4>What is Universal SSL?</h4>
			<p><a target="blank" href="https://blog.cloudflare.com/introducing-universal-ssl/" >Universal SSL</a> is the set of certificates that Cloudflare freely orders for all domains on Cloudflare so that visitors can access domains on Cloudflare safely and securely using the <a target="blank" target="blank" href="https://blog.cloudflare.com/introducing-http2/" >latest technologies</a>.</p>
			<h4>Why would I disable Universal SSL?</h4>
